  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some took up the Russian [? citizenship. ?] Most of them didn't took up the Russian citizenship.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they went-- sent all to Siberia, and they were-- they know how to do this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Amongst them was my-- my-- my brother in law.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Gdansk?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hella, my sister, my wife, my sister, and my son was born there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name is Ian Kaufman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ian Kaufman.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was born in 1945, in Danzig.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was born in June-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] September, sorry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The war was over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war was over, I was still in Gdansk, at part, only very shortly, in Radom.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, I was that time in Radom, when the war-- [INAUDIBLE] 1945 when the war was--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Radom, unfortunately, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was trying to take in possession back the tannery, my father's tannery.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I spent [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a good three months or more, even, a four months, trying [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] through the court.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beforehand the old institutions, what has got, because that was all still [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] half nationalized, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nationalized, I would say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That they are not against that I am getting back the factory, my father's factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I have to go through the court, even, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got papers here stating to bring me in as the owner of my father's factory.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
